title: The Gary Null Show
content:
On today’s show, the latest in health and healing including what happens when you take antacids, new information on... <!--more--> healthy pregnancy, and benefits of pomegranate.
Then, poverty’s impact on brain development.
Also, inequality in poverty on the rise in New Jersey, the number of homeless students increasing, and the 12 most pesticide laden fruits and vegetables.
Then, how deadly are medical errors?
Plus, meat is destroying the world and how we are becoming more of a police state.
And more!
